subject: Fiesta Bowl
Bowl Games
Suspensions, Dismissals and Resignations
Football (College)
lead_paragraph: Officials of the Fiesta Bowl, whose president was fired after being accused of misusing funds, will meet April 28 with the N.C.A.A. subcommittee in charge of licensing bowl games.
